<div class="container" id="about-us">
	<div class="row">
		<h1 class="about text-center" style="font-size:40px;">ABOUT US</h1>
    <p>
     &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Not sure where to take your group? Trouble collecting payment for large orders from groups members?
    </p>
		<p>
     &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Despite individual online ticketing, tickets for students, alumni, senior, church, corporate, and family groups are still sold over the phone by an organization's group sales manager. GroupEt is the first online marketplace for selling, searching, and purchasing discounted group tickets directly from venues. Any group of 5 or more --whether a group of your friends or formal affiliation -- is eligible to purchase group tickets on GroupEt.
		</p>
    <p style="margin-top:20px;">
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Our enhanced search allows you to find performances, exhibitions, or sports that match your date and your budget. It is finally possible to compare deals for specific dates/times across different genres of arts and entertainment.
		</p>
    <p>
     &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The bigger your group, the better deals you will find!
    </p>
    <p>
     &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;As the group leader, you can invite your group members to contribute to the final order to save you time and give you peace of mind.
    </p>
    <p>
     &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To get started, simply register for an account, set your designated city, and use the various search criteria to filter for your next perfect group outing.
    </p>
	</div>
