			<i>
			<p>
      GroupEt is designed to help connect arts and entertainment patrons with local venues, and provide greater exposure to arts organizations. There are no costs to using the service! Our fees are straightforward:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>
					Consumers pay a simple $5 booking fee for orders up to 50 tickets.$10 for orders exceeding 50 tickets.
				</li>
				<li>
					Non-profit merchants are charged only a $10 commissing on the final sale. Other merchants are charged a 10-25% commission.
				</li>
			</ul>
			</i>
